<tr><td colspan="2"><p class="smg">Introduction</p></td></tr>

<tr><td class="underline" colspan="2"><img height="1" alt="" src="../images/spacer.gif" width="1" /></td></tr> 

<tr><td width="435">
<p class="intro-people" style="margin-bottom:0">Our <em>People</em> section includes hundreds of entries on key personalities from Britain's film and television industries, both in front of and behind the camera.</p>
</td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="740" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td><p style="margin:0">Many of our authoritative biographies have been licensed from <em>The Encyclopedia of British Cinema</em> (ed. Brian McFarlane, Methuen, 2003) and from <em>Directors in British and Irish Cinema: A reference companion</em>  (ed. Robert Murphy, BFI, 2006). Others have been specially written for <em>BFI Screenonline</em>.</p></td>

